<section>
  <h2 id="motivation-for-technologies">Motivation for Technologies</h2>

  <p><strong>Why use JavaScript, Node.js and Express over Ruby and Ruby on Rails or Python and Django?</strong></p>

  <ol>
    <li class="fragment">only <strong>one language to learn</strong> throughout the course for server side development, front end development&#8230; and even database queries</li>
    <li class="fragment"><strong>straightforward to install</strong> entire stack (node, mongodb) on Windows, Linux and OSX</li>
    <li class="fragment">seems like a <strong>skill set that&#39;s currently sought after</strong> (former students are working with these technologies professionally!)</li>
    <li class="fragment">a <strong>fun</strong> stack to learn (really!)</li>
  </ol>

  <p class="fragment"><br /> 
The concepts and theory remain the same across this and other <em>technology stacks</em>, so what you learn here is applicable to Ruby, Python, etc. too!</p>
</section>

