<section>
  <h2 id="required-software">Required Software</h2>

  <h3 id="nodejs-obvs">Node.js (obvs)</h3>

  <ol>
    <li>Suggested install - use the package manager on your OS
      <ul>
        <li><strong>OSX</strong>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/Homebrew/homebrew/wiki/Installation">install</a> <a href="http://brew.sh/">homebrew</a></li>
            <li>
              <pre><code data-trim="" contenteditable="">brew install node</code></pre>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Linux</strong> (Specifically Debian/Ubuntu)
          <ul>
            <li>
              <pre><code data-trim="" contenteditable="">sudo apt-get install nodejs
sudo apt-get install npm</code></pre>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Use the Node.js installer:
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Windows</strong>, <strong>OSX</strong>, and <strong>Linux</strong>: see the <a href="http://nodejs.org/">downloads page on the Node.js site</a></li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

